  <brief_title>Efficacy, Safety, and PK of LX9211 in Patients With Diabetic Peripheral Neuropathic Pain</brief_title>
  <acronym>RELIEF-DPN 1</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Parallel-group, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety, and Pharmacokinetics of LX9211 in the Treatment of Diabetic Peripheral Neuropathic Pain</official_title>
