  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of the efficacy of a low and high dose of LX9211 compared to placebo in reducing&#xD;
      pain related to diabetic peripheral neuropathy over an 11 week assessment period.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
